 <span data-ttu-id="39aea-105">若要运行前面的代码示例，需要一个名为的级联样式表 (CSS) `Stylesheet.css` ，其中包含以下代码，与您的网站保存在同一目录中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="39aea-105">To run the preceding code example, you need a cascading style sheet (CSS) named `Stylesheet.css`, containing the following code, saved in the same directory as your Web site.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
body {  
  padding-left: 11em;  
  font-family:  Verdana, "Times New Roman",  
        Times, serif;  
  color: blue;  
  background-color: silver }  
h1 {  
  font-family: Helvetica, Geneva, Arial,  
        SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;   
  color: purple }  
```  
  
```csharp  
